data.description: Historic Queen Anne Victorian Home. Custom built in oak kitchen cabinets, island, bay window seating,  and office space in oversized kitchen. Turret in master. Two additional rooms upstairs for an office space and or laundry on same level as bedrooms.
data.whatILove: This home has a spectacular backyard and deck with amazing sunset views all year long. A workspace in the basement, an over sized garage and two porches. The woodwork is spectacular. Also, this home has a ton of storage space with a walk up attic, cellar, nook underneath the steps on main level, etc.
